价为 130 美元，但当 WD 型号更便宜时，没有理由购买它。）这两种卡仍然比<a data-i13n="cpos:58;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-ps5-ssd-expansion-upgrade-150052315.html">同类 SSD</a>贵，但任何节省都值得欢迎。</p><h2>索尼 PlayStation VR2 </h2><p><core-commerce id="e08afe95d37e4696b6f3ea896e241164" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Prime Big Deal Days 为<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:59;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL1BsYXlTdGF0aW9uLVZSMi1QU1ZSMi01L2RwL0IwQzFRSjZWSFk_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWpkLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkZGM3ZTNkMC0xYWM1LTRhMTMtYTYwZC1iZTgwZjU3ZGI3OGMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAcmDYmSI3lgpALrOyEhACPj1WCms8hg-qhiV60vBGKij&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPlayStation-VR2-PSVR2-5%2Fdp%2FB0C1QJ6VHY" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/PlayStation-VR2-PSVR2-5/dp/B0C1QJ6VHY">索尼今年 2 月发布的 PlayStation VR2</a>耳机带来了首次大幅折扣。目前价格降至 509 美元，比标价低 41 美元。对于 PS5 上没有超级丰富的游戏库的 VR 耳机来说，这仍然是一个很大的变化，但如果你一直在犹豫是否要购买该设备，那么它至少更容易接受。我们在 PSVR2 发布时给了<a data-i13n="cpos:60;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/playstation-vr2-review-great-headset-should-be-cheaper-130032254.html">84 分的评价</a>，因为它出色的双 OLED 显示屏、（相对）舒适的佩戴和精良的控制器给我们留下了深刻的印象。</p><h2> HyperX 云毒刺 2 </h2><p><core-commerce id="c2950c5f78b543368110f7757b2a069d" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>我们的<a data-i13n="cpos:61;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-headset-130006477.html">最佳游戏耳机</a>指南中的最佳预算选择是<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:62;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbi