 data-i13n="cpos:68;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-headset-130006477.html">最佳游戏耳机</a>指南中推荐 HD 560S：其开放式设计会引入并泄漏大量噪音，但其宽广的声场和平衡的特征为游戏带来令人愉悦的沉浸感。长时间佩戴也很舒适。只是不要对深沉的低音抱有太多期望。</p><h2>雷蛇猎魂 V2 TKL </h2><p><core-commerce id="d37ab4a9481f4468ae1d5828c76e0bdd" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:69;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOUMxMlE4RFg_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWpkLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkZGM3ZTNkMC0xYWM1LTRhMTMtYTYwZC1iZTgwZjU3ZGI3OGMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAQ2smGH-KzbZ7txM22mZFc1W5fUrwFcnQvwtdOr3brXf&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09C12Q8DX" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09C12Q8DX?th=1">Razer Huntsman V2 TKL</a>售价 90 美元，比市场平均售价低 30 美元左右。这是我们<a data-i13n="cpos:70;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-keyboard-140019954.html">最佳游戏键盘</a>指南中的一个选择，因为我们喜欢它清爽的 PBT 键帽、坚固的框架、干净的 RGB 灯光、包括腕托和稳定的性能。问题是，这笔交易适用于配备 Razer <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Razer;elmt:;cpos:71;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=d043077a-4ba1-4321-a933-30b8701d8d31&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Razer&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5yYXplci5jb20vcmF6ZXItb3B0aWNhbC1zd2l0Y2giLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImRkYzdlM2QwLTFhYzUtNGExMy1hNjBkLWJlODBmNTdkYjc4YyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAUMFPuZ-qGoZOiL7wx0neBOe4t2mUeowrlykep7uJOrh&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.razer.com%2Frazer-optical-switch" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.razer.com/razer-optical-switch">Clicky Optical 开关</a>的型号，我们发现它比线性开关噪音更大、声音更刺耳。这两种型号都不可热插拔。但如果您能忍受更大的打字声，那么还有很多值得您喜欢的地方。 Razer 最近发布了更高端的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Razer;elmt:;cpos:72;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=d043077a-4ba1-4321-a933-30b8701d8d31&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Razer&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5yYXplci5jb20vcGMvZ2FtaW5nLWtleWJvYXJkcy9odW50c21hbi1saW5lIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkZGM3ZTNkMC0xYWM1LTRhMTMtYTYwZC1iZTgwZjU3ZGI3OGMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAARaC0VJ7GhriAr-yx5WclfIGgykI7GiP4MGKYUc3ZcPA&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.razer.com%2Fpc%2Fgaming-keyboards%2Fhuntsman-line" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.razer.com/pc/gaming-keyboards/huntsman-line">Huntsman V3 Pro 系列</a>，但这些产品并没有打折。</p><h2> SteelSeries Apex Pro TKL 无线</h2><p><core-commerce id="cf5e53452b004732a04b11f270e2e4f8" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:73;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQkY2N0RNNks_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWpkLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkZGM3ZTNkMC0xYWM1LTRhMTMtYTYwZC1iZTgwZjU3ZGI3OGMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAUChi8yYVHzpvOwzog2wHJYAyL9R5vAFAMdwMYI2GtRz&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BF67DM6K" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BF67DM6K">SteelSeries Apex Pro TKL Wireless</a>售价降至 175 美元，距离历史最低价不到 1 美元，比标价低 75 美元。这是我们的<a data-i13n="cpos:74;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-keyboard-140019954.html">游戏键盘购买指南</a>中的首选无线选择，主要是因为它的磁性 OmniPoint 开关可以实现一系列有用的游戏功能。例如，您可以升高或降低各个按键的驱动点 - 设置高点以使打字更舒适，或设置低点以使按键响应更灵敏 - 并使用<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:SteelSeries;elmt:;cpos:75;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=e8351d9d-883b-4d2b-9ca2-def694c65fa7&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=SteelSeries&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3N0ZWVsc2VyaWVzLmNvbS9ibG9nL2V4cGxhaW5pbmctcmFwaWQtdHJpZ2dlci1uZXctc3RlZWxzZXJpZXMta2V5Ym9hcmQtZmVhdHVyZS05OTEiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImRkYzdlM2QwLTFhYzUtNGExMy1hNjBkLWJlODBmNTdkYjc4YyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAZ-JkkrBfP8D1Y5vzi3gmNjO89PSMZK7DioA5KSqzA0B&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fsteelseries.com%2Fblog%2Fexplaining-rapid-trigger-new-steelseries-keyboard-feature-991" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://steelseries.com/blog/explaining-rapid-trigger-new-steelseries-keyboard-feature-991">快速触发</a>模式更快地重复输入。</p><p>键盘的其余部分也令人满意，有多种连接选项和一个用于调整设置的有用的 OLED 显示屏，尽管你购买它的原因更多是因为它的游戏功能而不是打字体验。总的来说，我们认为<a data-i13n="cpos:76;pos:1" href="https://wooting.io/wooting-60he">Wooting 60HE</a>对于游戏爱好者来说是更好的选择，但该产品并未发售；如果您需要无线连接，Apex Pro 是一个足够接近的替代品。较小的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:77;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQjE2SkZGNTQ_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWpkLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkZGM3ZTNkMC0xYWM1LTRhMTMtYTYwZC1iZTgwZjU3ZGI3OGMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAcA08gwQ8KNN9QHS-Nm_j5o43qp0DDDAI1983gxjgpbm&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0B16JFF54" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0B16JFF54">Apex Pro Mini Wireless</a>也有 15 美元的折扣。</p><h2>华硕 ROG Azoth </h2><p><core-commerce id="84d5dd5be0e74a8a883d4728b2655aeb" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>另一款高端无线游戏键盘<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:78;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQlNLWDhXM0I_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWpkLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkZGM3ZTNkMC0xYWM1LTRhMTMtYTYwZC1iZTgwZjU3ZGI3OGMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAZx3rRZ7GkwHXoQWtEmPA7cPDmt5O18Kd26FMtZdrAz3&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BSKX8W3B" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BSKX8W3B?th=1">ASUS ROG Azoth 的</a>各种开关配置售价为 210 美元。虽然这并不是历史最低价，但比该设备自今年早些时候上市以来的通常价格低了约 20 美元。我们在<a data-i13n="cpos:79;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-keyboard-140019954.html">游戏键盘指南</a>中将 ROG Azoth 列为荣誉奖。它价格昂贵，但制作精良，具有发烧友级别的风格，例如垫片安装设计（使击键感觉更柔和），以及包装盒中用于润滑开关的工具包。它没有上面的 Apex Pro 那样灵活的游戏功能，但它仍然绝对是优质的。</p><h2>三星 Evo 选择</h2><p><core-commerce id="9fca0a6c457049c7b633c5c81c6a5ecb" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:80;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOUIxSE1KOVo_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWpkLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkZGM3ZTNkMC0xYWM1LTRhMTMtYTYwZC1iZTgwZjU3ZGI3OGMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAV-QNIsEWqjrPLOYuu8t4-9h67Bzu6TiGhC9FN0-Z22k&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09B1HMJ9Z" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09B1HMJ9Z?th=1">三星 Evo Select</a> microSD 卡的 512GB 版本售价为 28 美元，创下历史新低，比平常价格低 7 美元。与此同时， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:81;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featu