配有两个支持 144Hz 4K 的 HDMI 2.1 端口。它还具有其他适合游戏的功能，例如<a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://www.hdmi.org/spec21sub/variablerefreshrate">VRR</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://www.hdmi.org/spec21sub/autolowlatencymode">ALLM</a> ，此外它还支持所有主要的 HDR 格式。它看起来仍然不像好的 OLED 设备那样丰富或流畅，而且可视角度也较差，但相对较低的价格应该有助于弥补这一点。</p><h2>海信U6K </h2><p><core-commerce id="3e87cbb6116f4a7b95d514d640393579" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:22;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzZXTFdRNVI_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWo5LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJjZDU1MmIzMC01MzAxLTQ2N2MtODMwYi1hMDNiOTc2NTA0MzEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAARyA5NqDxVVqDveD0rMEiDGwQ9Q2DkgKofRHEwjpxgcp&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0C6WLWQ5R" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C6WLWQ5R?th=1">海信 U6K</a>也在促销， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:23;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzZXTFdRNVI_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWo5LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJjZDU1MmIzMC01MzAxLTQ2N2MtODMwYi1hMDNiOTc2NTA0MzEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAARyA5NqDxVVqDveD0rMEiDGwQ9Q2DkgKofRHEwjpxgcp&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0C6WLWQ5R" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C6WLWQ5R?th=1">55 英寸</a>和<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:24;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-029