matches a Prime member-only deal it hit a few weeks ago and makes this a new low price for the public at large. It has a waterproof design, can recharge your phone, and at 13 pounds, it&#39;s big but still portable.</p><h2> JBL Go 2 </h2><p><core-commerce id="1c2652381cd9441a830c6ca8eb1217b8" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The tiny <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:23;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOEw5UkJNWUo_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNHN0LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI0YjAzMmI2MC1jNjM0LTQ2NWUtOGYyOS0wOTcxMGY4MDdiMTIifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAeFhDzykCgltTLMD63L7jSEQScEbIYlmHUa6hjVL50n3&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08L9RBMYJ" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08L9RBMYJ?th=1">JBL Go 3</a> also made its way into our October Prime day roundup for deals under $50. While we didn&#39;t test it for our Bluetooth speaker <a data-i13n="cpos:24;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-portable-bluetooth-speakers-133004551.html">guide</a> , we&#39;ve used and recommended plenty of JBL speakers. The Go 3 is 50 percent off, or $25 right now. You can also get the <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:25;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzI4OUZENlk_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNHN0LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI0YjAzMmI2MC1jNjM0LTQ2NWUtOGYyOS0wOTcxMGY4MDdiMTIifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAeaq-pyWaBEQf7_781eVJIko28z2lapZX4_Y81dcFS7f&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A