h any task you throw at it — and since the Air works with keyboard accessories, it could be a decent laptop replacement when on the go.</p><h2> Apple iPad mini </h2><p><core-commerce id="2dcd570265f0405288e58bae92396cc3" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOUc5MUxYRlA_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNHNzLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJhYmNkMDYzMi1lYjE3LTQ0ODctOWEwMS05YTBjMmEyZDdiY2YifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAfrCLQRT4gkr7x_fFuEpnfne0iS2L9HHHMC_wJODdZb_&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09G91LXFP" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09G91LXFP">Apple iPad mini</a> has dropped to $400 for October Prime Day. It&#39;s the <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-ipads-how-to-pick-the-best-apple-tablet-for-you-150054066.html">best small tablet</a> on the market right now and really your only option if you want a true one-hand-friendly iPad. It&#39;s powered by Apple&#39;s A15 Bionic chip and sports a TouchID-toting power button, solid cameras, a good battery life and a USB-C port for charging.</p><h2> Google Pixel Tablet </h2><p><core-commerce id="cd095ca4f60049368c6cfc6aaadb2869" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzFTSEdIU1o_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNHNzLTIwIiwiY29ud